OOC: Although i still need Soulstice, Jer, and Rudra to tell me what happened 
to my characters, i will start posting for who i have.

:::Ratchet/Sideswipe/Orion/Wheeljack/Starscream:::

::My Maximals wake up from their long rest::
Ratchet: Im itching to get back to work!
Sideswipe:Yeah, it's time we got moving again.
Orion: Then let's go!
Ratchet(comm): Hey Iron Raptor, is there anything we can do?
~~~~~
::Wheeljack, well satisfied by the day's work, decided to relax for awhile, 
so he got on his reclining chair and just felt proud of himself::
~~~~~
::Starscream looks to Drillbit::
Starscream: What should we do now?
